               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, Dawit, ዳዊት፡ with the Psalter of the Virgin; Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ፡, EMML 3213
                    The layout of the book and especially the colophon (see below)
                    confirms that this manuscript is EMML 3213. The catalogue entry is
                    published in volume 8, p. 157. The EMML project’s Bulletin of
                    Ethiopian Manuscripts, IX:1 (January 1982), p. 15, indicates that the
                    manuscript was shot in 1975. It is said to be from the church of
                    Kassat Michael, Warana Basso, Shoa, in the region of Ankobarr. At
                    the time of its microfilming it had none of the illuminations listed
                    above
                  </summary>
